Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:35.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look up at the sky,like a bird without wings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:40.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to fly,feeling your breath,release yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:45.23,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you sigh？Just count your blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:53.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every time you try,find something relieve yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:04.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mission is gonna be a tough one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:07.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's not a game any more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:13.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that I'll never fall again,girls don't wanna regret any more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.87,0:01:19.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can u hear I'm calling you,I just wanna feel you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:24.71,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to remember,so please remember
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:30.39,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you are calling me,I want you to feel me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:35.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know I won't surrender,I never surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:38.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mission,I've got to execute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:41.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's not a game any more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:47.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that I'll never fall again,girls don't wanna regret any more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:58.79,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Secrets of the Goddess －God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:35.30,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望穹碧 如鳥失其翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:40.97,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若欲飛起 感受微風 放鬆自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:45.23,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緣何歎息？世界如此美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:53.27,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每每嘗試 尋其深意 堅信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:04.69,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使命不易
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:07.40,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知此再非遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:13.64,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓不復言敗 因不願後悔莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.87,0:01:19.11,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的呼喚能否觸及你？我只想去感受你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:24.71,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切勿忘卻回憶 故請於心銘記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:30.39,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽見了你 想讓你感受我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:35.99,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知我不會放棄 絕不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:38.70,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務勢在必行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:41.41,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知此再非遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:47.32,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓不復言敗 因不願後悔莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:58.79,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神的秘密 －只有神知道
